data.description: Immaculate single story Woodside former model home is a must see. No details were missed. 3 spacious bedrooms, plus an office with custom built in wall unit, large family room with custom built in wall unit as well. Stunning kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, dining area plus a formal dining room, inside laundry room with sink and cabinets, washer and dryer included as well. Highly upgraded wood floors, custom window coverings, fully landscaped front and back yards with designer patio slab. Tandum 3 car garage. Ask agent about closing cost incentives and the 10 year home warranty!!!!
